quran[4]{c,v,t,f}:
  7,156,"Kí O sì kọ àkọsílẹ̀ rere fún wa ní ayé yìí àti ní ọ̀run. Dájúdájú àwa ṣẹ́rí padà sí ọ̀dọ̀ Rẹ.” (Allāhu) sọ pé: “Ìyà Mi, Mo ń fi jẹ ẹni tí Mo bá fẹ́. Àti pé ìkẹ́ Mi gbòòrò ju gbogbo n̄ǹkan. Èmi yó sì kọ (ìkẹ́ Mi) mọ́ àwọn tó ń bẹ̀rù (Mi), tí wọ́n sì ń yọ Zakāh àti àwọn tí wọ́n ní ìgbàgbọ́ òdodo nínú àwọn āyah Wa.”",""
  7,157,"Àwọn tó ń tẹ̀lé Òjíṣẹ́ náà, Ànábì aláìmọ̀ọ́nkọmọ̀ọ́nkà, ẹni tí wọ́n yóò bá àkọsílẹ̀ nípa rẹ̀ lọ́dọ̀ wọn nínú at-Taorāh àti al-’Injīl, tí ó ń pa wọ́n láṣẹ ohun rere, tí ó ń kọ ohun burúkú fún wọn, tí ó ń ṣe àwọn n̄ǹkan dáadáa ní ẹ̀tọ́ fún wọn, tí ó sì ń ṣe àwọn n̄ǹkan àìdáa ní èèwọ̀ fún wọn, tí ó tún máa gbé ẹrù (àdéhùn tó wúwo) àti àjàgà tó ń bẹ lọ́rùn wọn<sup>1</sup> kúrò fún wọn; àwọn tó bá gbàgbọ́ nínú rẹ̀, tí wọ́n bu iyì fún un, tí wọ́n ràn án lọ́wọ́, tí wọ́n sì tẹ̀lé ìmọ́lẹ̀ náà (ìyẹn, al-Ƙur’ān) tí A sọ̀kalẹ̀ fún un, àwọn wọ̀nyẹn, àwọn ni olùjèrè.","[1] “Àjàgà ọrùn wọn ni èyí tí Allāhu - tó ga jùlọ - gbékọ́ ọrùn ọwọ́ wọn nígbà tí wọ́n wí pé “Dídì ni ọwọ́ Allāhu wà” gẹ́gẹ́ bí Allāhu - tó ga jùlọ - ṣe fi rinlẹ̀ nínú sūrah al-Mọ̄’dah; 5:64.” (Tọbariy)"
  7,158,"Sọ pé: “Ẹ̀yin ènìyàn, dájúdájú èmi ni Òjíṣẹ́ Allāhu sí gbogbo yín pátápátá. (Allāhu) Ẹni tó ni ìjọba àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀. Kò sí ọlọ́hun kan tí a gbọ́dọ̀ jọ́sìn fún ní ọ̀nà òdodo àyàfi Òun. Ó ń sọ ẹ̀dá di alààyè. Ó sì ń sọ ẹ̀dá di òkú. Nítorí náà, ẹ gbàgbọ́ nínú Allāhu àti Òjíṣẹ́ Rẹ̀. Ànábì aláìmọ̀ọ́nkọmọ̀ọ́nkà, ẹni tó gbàgbọ́ nínú Allāhu àti àwọn ọ̀rọ̀ Rẹ̀. Ẹ tẹ̀lé e nítorí kí ẹ lè mọ̀nà.”",""
  7,159,"Ó wà nínú ìjọ (Ànábì) Mūsā, ìjọ kan tó ń fi òdodo tọ́ (àwọn ènìyàn) sọ́nà. Wọ́n sì ń ṣe ẹ̀tọ́ pẹ̀lú rẹ̀.<sup>1</sup>","[1] Àwọn wọ̀nyẹn ni Allāhu - tó ga jùlọ - sọ nípa wọn nínú sūrah al-Mọ̄’idah; 5:83-85."
